    "date": "2026-05-16",
    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **CLI LaTeX digit-base superscripts + grouped scripts.** delimiter-less\n  ÏàòÏãù detector Í∞Ä `10^2`, `10^-3`, `10^(R_j - R_i)` Ï≤òÎüº Ïà´Ïûê base Î•º\n  Í∞ÄÏßÑ superscript ÌëúÌòÑÏùÑ inline math Î°ú ÏäπÍ≤©Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. `^(...)` /\n  `^{...}` ÎÇ¥Î∂ÄÏùò nested `_j` Îäî Î∞îÍπ• superscript Î∞©Ìñ•ÏùÑ Îî∞Îùº ` ≤` Î°ú\n  Î≥ÄÌôòÎêòÏñ¥ `10‚ÅΩ·¥ø ≤‚Åª·¥ø‚Å±‚Åæ` / `10·¥ø ≤‚Åª·¥ø‚Å±` Î°ú Î≥¥Ïù¥Î©∞, braced superscript Ïùò\n  Î≥µÌï© payload Ïóê bracket fallback Ïù¥ ÏûòÎ™ª ÏÝÅÏö©ÎêòÏñ¥ `10[...]` Î°ú Íπ®ÏßÄÎäî\n  ÌöåÍ∑ÄÎ•º ÎßâÏïòÏäµÎãàÎã§. `1_000`, `snake_case`, path false positive Îäî Í≥ÑÏÜç\n  text Î°ú ÎÇ®ÏäµÎãàÎã§.\n- **CLI LaTeX digit-base superscripts + grouped scripts.** The\n  delimiter-less math detector now promotes digit-base superscripts such\n  as `10^2`, `10^-3`, and `10^(R_j - R_i)` to inline math. Nested `_j`\n  markers inside `^(...)` / `^{...}` inherit the outer superscript\n  direction, rendering as `10‚ÅΩ·¥ø ≤‚Åª·¥ø‚Å±‚Åæ` / `10·¥ø ≤‚Åª·¥ø‚Å±`, and complex braced\n  superscripts no longer hit the broken `10[...]` bracket fallback.\n  False positives such as `1_000`, `snake_case`, and paths stay as text."
